This repo contains dvipdf and supporting files.

-----------------------------

Put *.pfb files from the following archives to this directory:

https://www.ams.org/arc/tex/amsfonts.zip
https://mirrors.ctan.org/fonts/ps-type1/cm-super.zip

-----------------------------

To correctly copy/search quoteright, quoteleft and minus,
change ghostscript source:

1)
In the end of function pdf_simple_font_needs_ToUnicode change
'return false' to 'return true'

2)
sed -i '/ quoteright\b/{s// SP050000/;n};s/SP050000/quoteright/' Resource/Decoding/Unicode
sed -i '/ quoteleft\b/{s// SD130000/;n};s/SD130000/quoteleft/'   Resource/Decoding/Unicode
sed -i '/ minus\b/{s// SP100000/;n};s/SP100000/minus/'           Resource/Decoding/Unicode

Build:

With dpkg-buildpackage)
apt-get source ghostscript
sudo apt-get build-dep ghostscript
dpkg-buildpackage -r fakeroot -b -uc -us
Delete PATH from dvipdf

Witout dpkg-buildpackage)
./configure --without-x --prefix=$HOME/lhplain/ghostscript
make
make install

(To see the effect of this, add -dCompressFonts=false to ps2pdf,
open pdf file via 'less' and search CMap.)
